			>
			I really like the idea, but I'm sure that it would be seen as bad for game balance. Player-crafted charms, for instance, would bring a lot more into the game at lower levels than you currently see. Player-crafted augments would likely be ungodly difficult to make (355 skill), require all sorts of stuff dropping from deep in GoD (blech!) and even that wouldn't be enough to make the developers think that they weren't unbalancing. But it is a great idea!
