			<P>What I'd really like to see is the ability to trade-back-in LDoN augs we don't need anymore.&nbsp; Trade in for partial % of LDoN points returned.&nbsp; Sucks when you work so hard for an ER aug and then you get a major loot drop with that effect or higher.&nbsp; Then you just trash your aug and never use it again?</P>
<P>Also would like to see and ON/OFF function to enable/disable tribute system, so don't have to run to home town just to start it up.&nbsp; Purchase it in home, then wherever you are, send a pigeon(or whatever) to turn off/on the tribute stats..&nbsp; This is the one big reason why I am not using it.</P>
<P>If it's already there, please someone slap me around and tell me how to do it. hehehe</P>
